---
description: Proto file formatting
globs: *.proto
alwaysApply: false
---
When generating or refactoring proto file adhere to the following rules

- Always add simple and useful comments where possible.
- Ensure that comment at the top of the file is present to show how to compile the proto file to generate files for Go and C++.
- Ensure that the Makefile (at the project root) handles proto conversion properly.